      <title>设置root密码</title>
      <link href="/2019/07/23/Ubuntu-Root-Password/"/>
      <url>/2019/07/23/Ubuntu-Root-Password/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>刚安装完 Ubuntu 后, 使用su命令不能切换到root用户<br>这个时候需要先设置root用户的密码。</p><p>输入下面的命令设置root用户的密码:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo passwd root</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>会要求输入当前用户的密码, 然后就可以设置新密码了(输入两次)<br>当提示 password updated successfully 就代表成功了</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">haofeng@ubuntu:~$ sudo passwd root</span><br><span class="line">[sudo] password <span class="keyword">for</span> haofeng:</span><br><span class="line">Enter new UNIX password: </span><br><span class="line">Retype new UNIX password: </span><br><span class="line">passwd: password updated successfully</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以后就可以输入下面的命令切换用户了</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">su root</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
